					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-2167087#post-2769323</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-2167087/scp-2734#post-2769323</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 17 Mar 2017 03:56:41 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>BewareTheDragon</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3010189</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>While I cannot help but feel as though this is in reference to the clowns that were running around terrorizing people last year, it's still different enough and just flat-out weird enough to make itself something that will last even when people have forgotten about the 'killer clowns'. I was expecting it to just be about 'killer clowns' at first, but I was pleasantly surprised when it turned out that the clowns were herbivorous and pacifistic. +1 from me for the oddity of vanishing clowns that <em>don't</em> kill people.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
